This post originally began from me wanting to share that keeping a single screen working helps me fight the urge to multi-task during meetings (and it's very strong, trust me). Now I also want to share other tools/methods that help me stay engaged during calls, keep track of my tasks (as a manager, I don't have my work in a team Rally/Jira anymore) and keep track of the important things.

